  "description": "<div id=\"product-detail\">\n<h4>Application:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>2012-2017 Land Rover - Range Rover Evoque with EcoBoost 2.0T Gen.1 Engine</li>\n<li>2015-2017 Land Rover - Discovery Sport with EcoBoost 2.0T Gen.1 Engine</li>\n<li>2013-2015 Land Rover - LR2 with EcoBoost 2.0T Gen.1 Engine</li>\n<li>2013-2017 Jaguar XF with EcoBoost 2.0T Gen.1 Engine</li>\n<li>2016-2017 Jaguar XE with EcoBoost 2.0T Gen.1 Engine</li>\n<li>2013-2014 Ford Focus ST with EcoBoost 2.0T Gen.1 Engine</li>\n<li>2012-2014 Volvo S60 with EcoBoost 2.0T Gen.1 Engine</li>\n<li>2013-2014 Volvo V60 with EcoBoost 2.0T Gen.1 Engine</li>\n<li>2012-2014 Volvo XC60 with EcoBoost 2.0T Gen.1 Engine</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Features:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>High quality replacements for factory parts; excellent quality and durability, optimizing vehicle performance</li>\n<li>OE design, simple replacement for factory part</li>\n<li>Center rotating bearing housing designed to work with factory oil and coolant lines</li>\n<li>Component balanced dynamically (avg 0.5 mg or less) using state-of-the-art balancing machine</li>\n<li>Turbine housing made of ductile iron QT450-10, withstands temperatures up to 700°C</li>\n<li>Steel turbine wheel made from K418 alloy for high oxidation resistance, stable under high temperatures up to 900°C</li>\n<li>Cast aluminum blades with good air tightness and corrosion resistance</li>\n<li>Accessories in the photos are included</li>\n<li>1 year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n<li><em>Professional installation is highly recommended</em></li>\n<li><em>Before installation, ensure the cause of turbo failure is analyzed and eliminated (e.g., insufficient oil supply, foreign objects in intake, crankcase ventilation issues)</em></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Technical Specifications:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Durable Compressor Wheel: 12 (6+6) blades, Size: 41*51*53.5 mm</li>\n<li>Turbine Wheel: 9 blades, Size: 40.4*45 mm</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Turbo Part Numbers:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>AG9N-6K682-AF / AG9N-6K682-AG / AG9N-6K682-AH / AG9N-6K682-AJ / AG9N-6K682-AK / AG9N-6K682-AL / AG9N-6K682-AM</li>\n<li>BG9E-6K682-AB / BG9E-6K682-AC / BG9E-6K682-AD / BG9E-6K682-AE / BG9E-6K682-AF / BG9E-6K682-AG</li>\n<li>5217313, 5131579, 5148290, 5157826, 7404261, 5169727, 5203374, 5154657, 5163623, 2205304</li>\n<li>V36001347, 36001347, V36001788, 36001788, V36001893, 36001893, V36002927, 36002927, V36002955, 36002955</li>\n<li>LR031510, LR045098, LR057362, LR075185</li>\n<li>53039700154, 53039700191, 53039700198, 53039700237, 53039700238, 53039700240, 53039700241, 53039700259</li>\n<li>53039700260, 53039700269, 53039700288, 53039700289</li>\n<li>53039880154, 53039880191, 53039880198, 53039880237, 53039880238, 53039880240, 53039880241, 53039880259</li>\n<li>53039880260, 53039880269, 53039880288, 53039880289</li>\n<li>53039880505, 53039900154, 53039900191, 53039900198, 53039900237, 53039900238, 53039900240, 53039900241</li>\n<li>53039900259, 53039900260, 53039900269, 53039900288, 53039900289</li>\n<li>K03-0154, K03-0191, K03-0198, K03-0237, K03-0238, K03-0240, K03-0241, K03-0259, K03-0260, K03-0269, K03-0288, K03-0289, K03-0505</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
